snippet.title: The Psychedelic Muse
snippet.description:
The Psychedelic Muse is a beckoning odyssey of deep chillout music, dedicated to chilling in mind, body, and spirit: psychill, progressive downtempo, ambient electronica, psydub & psybass - you can find it all here in our oasis of chill.

Subscribe for exclusive mixes, the latest music,  old-school chill classics, and much more. New chill for your auditory tranquility every day.

Hang out with our psychedelically-inclined cat and listen to music from Gabriel Le Mar, Pete Ardron, YOUTH, The Irresistible Force, The Flying Mars, Astropilot, StereOMantra, Lauge, Ovnimoon, Robert Elster, and more incredible downtempo talents. Part of Chill Space Network
